{"tid":798490,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"點睇啲KOL借小丸子名氣寫殺人故仔呃like而紅？","createTime":"2018-08-29T10:40:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-29T10:40:01.000Z","uid":191953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"719271c43a6a65bc7c31c1af6e1a96a710b88243","tid":798490,"uid":191953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T10:40:01.000Z","msg":"話說小丸子作者死左，諗返起上年有條KOL寫小丸子版嘅殺人故仔幾紅下。<br />\n<br />\n條KOL係作家莎比亞，呢家個page有十幾萬人like，唔知係唔係藍橘子個乜野大雄的葬禮紅左，佢就有樣學樣寫個故仔去屠殺小丸子啲同學，吸引人睇佢個page，點知又俾佢紅左喎。<br />\n<br />\n其實咁樣用人地故仔去二次創作寫小說去提高自己名氣，算唔算侵權？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/29/182932_ec95b0feba94819b699ecfebc1eeec85.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F29%2F182932_ec95b0feba94819b699ecfebc1eeec85.png&h=408fc46c&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}